title: Inside Delta Force
description:
Great book about the formation of Delta Force by Eric Haney.  This book was used as inspiration for the the TV show "The Unit".

All the copies of this book I found had lots of typos from the scanning and OCR process.  As I read it, I cleaned it up and generated this new version.

Very good read.  Buy a copy of the book if you like it to support the author!
